headline: TransDigm Group and Servotronics, Inc. Announce Acquisition Agreement
summary: TransDigm Group Incorporated ("TransDigm") (NYSE: TDG) and Servotronics, Inc. ("Servotronics") (NYSE American: SVT) today announced a definitive merger agreement providing for Servotronics to become an indirect wholly owned subsidiary of TransDigm. TransDigm designs, produces and supplies highly engineered aircraft components. Servotronics designs, produces and supplies highly engineered servo valves.
